

	 
       urlLink Drew Perry  has instructions for making a charger for an ipod out of three batteries and a deck of cards.  It's really cool but I'd like to see you try to take it on an airplane.  I bet even if you put it in your checked baggage, you'd end up in a room with one bare lightbulb getting very friendly with a guy or two from security who really don't believe you when you try to explain to them that there's nothing up there, so they really don't have to look.
    
